    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a benchmark of mechanical preservation. Powered by a naturally aspirated 3.8L flat-six with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), the powerplant exhibits perfect compression and a pristine valvetrain. The 6-speed manual transaxle offers short, notched throws with a clutch take-up that remains firm and communicative. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the chassis maintains its original torsional rigidity with zero bushing deflection. Every component, from the factory-spec cross-drilled rotors to the underbody aero-shielding, remains in showroom condition. This is a turn-key example for the purist seeking uncompromised longitudinal and lateral dynamics.",
      "price": 49250.0,
