      "description": "This is, quite simply, the finest example of this model currently on the market. Maintained in a climate-controlled garage and finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that remains entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections, this vehicle presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory scent; the premium leather upholstery shows absolutely no bolster wear, and the high-gloss wood trim is flawless. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the high-fidelity surround sound system, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, backed by a comprehensive service history performed exclusively through authorized dealerships. All original keys, manuals, and a pristine set of factory floor mats are included. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this car offers a true showroom experience.",
